          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Energy and Reduced Fatigue",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>More Green provides Vitamin B1, B3, and B5, which play a key role in converting food into usable energy for the body. By supporting efficient energy metabolism, they help reduce fatigue and promote sustained energy levels throughout the day. </p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_cJ8rQQ": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Immunity and Recovery",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>More Green delivers Vitamin B6 and B9, which play an important role in supporting the body’s immune function and cellular repair processes. These nutrients contribute to the production and maintenance of cells, helping the body recover efficiently and maintain overall resilience.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_FzwX9Y": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Skin and Hair Wellness",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>With Vitamin B7 (Biotin), More Green supports the maintenance of healthy skin and hair by nourishing the body at a cellular level. It helps convert nutrients into usable forms that contribute to stronger hair and healthier-looking skin.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_pzCmgz": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Cellular Protection",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>More Green contains Vitamin E and Vitamin B2, which act as antioxidants to help protect cells from oxidative stress caused by everyday environmental factors. By neutralizing harmful compounds, they support overall cellular health and long-term well-being.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_7ww9CL": {
