            "row_content": "<p>Iron, Potassium, and Magnesium in Moregreen support essential body functions, including oxygen transport, heart rhythm, and muscle activity. These minerals work together to maintain physiological balance and support overall body function.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
