    "multirow_nQEXpL": {
      "type": "multirow",
      "blocks": {
        "row_bWq3YA": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/conv_cb927c91-75f0-4f42-afc9-9e3e02fd0cb3.png",
            "caption": "",
            "heading": "What are Microgreens?",
            "text": "<p>Microgreens are young, nutrient-dense shoots of sunflower seeds, harvested within 7-10 days of germination, well before they become adult plants. They are considered a \"superfood\" because they are packed with higher (4 to 40x) concentrations of nutrients compared to fully grown greens. Loaded with protein, vitamins, minerals and antioxidants, they’re the perfect way to boost your energy and cover nutrition bases.</p><p>SMP is made from these fresh sunflower microgreens, dried and ground for easy use.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "row_VMefbQ": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Man_in_office_typing_202605041745.jpg",
            "caption": "",
            "heading": "The 3pm wall is not inevitable.",
            "text": "<p>Mid-afternoon energy crashes typically stem from blood sugar dips, insufficient B-vitamins for mitochondrial energy production, and magnesium depletion. More Green SMP addresses all three through sustained nutrition, not stimulants.<br/><br/>Full B-complex: cellular energy metabolism.<br/>295.95mg Magnesium: neuromuscular function and stress regulation.<br/>Slow-release carbohydrates: no spike, no crash.<br/><br/>One spoonful in your lunch. The difference by 3pm.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "row_86HTmy": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Sunflower_microgreens_and_lab_re__202605061736_30e46622-28b5-410f-84ba-e7efa75ebffe.jpg",
            "caption": "",
            "heading": "Grown here, Tested here. Certified before it reaches you.",
            "text": "<p>FSSAI License: Confirms they meet India's legal food safety standards.</p><p>NABL Accredited: This means the lab that tested the food is world-class and follows strict, internationally recognized protocols for accuracy.</p><p><strong>Full lab reports are available </strong><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1EKRuYsfRqEC8UdV7nnChT6RHc18xxXls?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"More Green's Sunflower Microgreen Powder Lab Reports\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>here</strong></span></a><strong>.</strong></p><p>The plants are grown in high-tech polyhouses that ensure consistent quality and purity.</p><p>Nature made it nutritious; our technology keeps it pure. By growing our produce in controlled vertical trays rather than open soil, we eliminate threats like heavy metals and pests. Advanced climate automation ensures the perfect temperature and humidity, preventing mold and fungus naturally without harsh chemicals.</p><p>To prove our promise, every package is backed by an independent lab test of that exact harvest. True transparency, from our farm to your fork.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        }
      },
